---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---
<Layout title="About | Notes on Tech" description="Learn about Alberto Ferreira de Melo and the story behind Notes on Tech.">
  <SiteHeader />
  <main>
    <article class="card bio">
      <h1>About Alberto</h1>
      <p>
        I’m a technologist and writer exploring how warm, human-centered design can make advanced technology feel more
        like a companion than a tool. After relocating to Sweden, I began capturing stories about the interplay between
        AI research, creative practice, and everyday Nordic life.
      </p>
      <p>
        This space is intentionally simple — a notebook for essays, prototypes, and reflections. Expect a mix of
        hands-on experiments, thoughtful commentary, and snapshots of life in Scandinavia.
      </p>
      <p>
        When I’m not writing, you’ll find me sketching interface ideas, testing new ML models, or cycling along the
        Swedish archipelago.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
  <SiteFooter />
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw + 1rem, 3rem);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .bio {
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 179, 71, 0.18), transparent 60%);
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }
</style>
